DANIEL PINCHBECK: Well,
what "The God Problem?"

00:23:15.116 --> 00:23:18.580 align:middle line:84%
"The God Problem" is
this-- if you're like me,

00:23:18.580 --> 00:23:21.930 align:middle line:84%
