of discarded material

00:38:16.150 --> 00:38:18.140 align:middle line:84%
en route to landfill
and employs artists

00:38:18.140 --> 00:38:20.880 align:middle line:84%
and designers to reconfigure
it into furniture and art.

00:38:20.880 --> 00:38:22.990 align:middle line:84%
REDU was a response to
years a bearing witness

00:38:22.990 --> 00:38:24.980 align:middle line:84%
to the massive amounts
of New York City waste

00:38:24.980 --> 00:38:26.880 align:middle line:90%
shipped off to landfills.

00:38:26.880 --> 00:38:29.760 align:middle line:10%
REDU's governing belief is with
the infusion of creativity,

00:38:29.760 --> 00:38:31.150 align:middle line:10%
there is no such
thing as garbage,

00:38:31.150 --> 00:38:33.370 align:middle line:10%
that garbage is a mentality.

00:38:33.370 --> 00:38:36.805 align:middle line:84%
For the last 15 years Amber
has worked on feature films, TV

00:38:36.805 --> 00:38:39.610 align:middle line:84%
