a range of talent including

00:38:39.610 --> 00:38:42.540 align:middle line:84%
Sam Sheppard, Sean
Penn, Woody Harrelson,

00:38:42.540 --> 00:38:46.150 align:middle line:84%
Mark Wahlberg, DMX, and the
Marley brothers, to name a few.

00:38:46.150 --> 00:38:48.470 align:middle line:84%
She Co-produced
"Raw for 30 Days,"

00:38:48.470 --> 00:38:51.130 align:middle line:84%
