on a raw food diet,

00:38:51.130 --> 00:38:53.820 align:middle line:84%
And is also developing
Mush, a raw food bar.

00:38:53.820 --> 00:38:55.280 align:middle line:84%
To add to this,
Amber is currently

00:38:55.280 --> 00:38:56.590 align:middle line:84%
forming a slate
for her production

00:38:56.590 --> 00:38:57.760 align:middle line:90%
company, Revisionary Films.

