00:39:25.850 --> 00:39:27.473 align:middle line:84%
Tell us a little bit
about what you do.

00:39:27.473 --> 00:39:28.872 align:middle line:84%
MIKI AGRAWAL: Sure.
-Miki?

00:39:28.872 --> 00:39:30.003 align:middle line:90%
