Without any experience,
yeah, whatsoever.

00:41:56.310 --> 00:41:59.130 align:middle line:90%


00:41:59.130 --> 00:42:01.440 align:middle line:84%
And now, you know, we-- I opened
my first tiny little place

00:42:01.440 --> 00:42:02.640 align:middle line:90%
in the Upper East Side.

00:42:02.640 --> 00:42:05.660 align:middle line:84%
And then opened my second
place in the West Village.

00:42:05.660 --> 00:42:08.430 align:middle line:84%
And now opening a big
location in downtown Vegas,

00:42:08.430 --> 00:42:10.040 align:middle line:84%
with Tony Hsieh, who's
the CEO of Zappos--

00:42:10.040 --> 00:42:12.440 align:middle line:84%
he's my business
partner-- and opening

