00:55:59.870 --> 00:56:03.010 align:middle line:84%
Now, if you can sell more than
just the piece of furniture.

00:56:03.010 --> 00:56:03.710 align:middle line:90%
The story.

00:56:03.710 --> 00:56:07.640 align:middle line:84%
If you can sell the story,
then, all of a sudden,

00:56:07.640 --> 00:56:10.110 align:middle line:84%
