technique of overlaying

00:56:26.420 --> 00:56:28.510 align:middle line:90%
15 different kinds of veneers.

00:56:28.510 --> 00:56:30.290 align:middle line:84%
He was capable of
doing that because

00:56:30.290 --> 00:56:34.330 align:middle line:84%
of a bunch of new technologies
