00:56:38.075 --> 00:56:39.780 align:middle line:90%
There's a whole story there.

00:56:39.780 --> 00:56:43.100 align:middle line:84%
And if you can tell the story,
that chair isn't just a chair.

00:56:43.100 --> 00:56:45.820 align:middle line:84%
That chair is a way of
connecting with your friends.

00:56:45.820 --> 00:56:47.600 align:middle line:90%
It's a way of showing off.

00:56:47.600 --> 00:56:49.520 align:middle line:90%
It's a way of getting attention.

00:56:49.520 --> 00:56:53.190 align:middle line:84%
And we don't just buy things
for their practical use.

00:56:53.190 --> 00:56:55.020 align:middle line:84%
We buy them for the
attention that they

00:56:55.020 --> 00:56:57.470 align:middle line:90%
will buy us from our friends.

00:56:57.470 --> 00:56:58.790 align:middle line:90%
And how do we get attention?

00:56:58.790 --> 00:57:00.470 align:middle line:84%
Waking up their
eyes, getting them

00:57:00.470 --> 00:57:01.940 align:middle line:90%
